<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Farmae | Online sales temporarily suspended</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Online sales are temporarily suspended. Orders placed until 08/05/2026 will be processed regularly."
    >
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --ink: #12202f;
        --muted: #5f6c7a;
        --line: rgba(18, 32, 47, 0.16);
        --surface: #edf6fb;
        --paper: #fffdf8;
        --accent: #126f9a;
        --accent-soft: #dceff7;
        --shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(18, 52, 78, 0.14);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        min-height: 100%;
        background: var(--surface);
      }

      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        font-family:
          Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
          "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        color: var(--ink);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 12% 12%, rgba(18, 111, 154, 0.18), transparent 30rem),
          linear-gradient(135deg, #f7fbff 0%, #dfeff7 100%);
      }

      main {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        padding: clamp(24px, 5vw, 72px);
      }

      .notice {
        width: min(1120px, 100%);
      }

      .brand {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 20px;
        margin-bottom: clamp(32px, 6vw, 72px);
      }

      .brand-name {
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1;
      }

      .brand-logo {
        display: block;
        width: clamp(150px, 18vw, 250px);
        height: auto;
      }

      .status {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 42px;
        padding: 0 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: var(--accent);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 650;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .header-actions {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 14px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: flex-end;
      }

      .contact-link {
        color: var(--ink);
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 650;
        text-decoration-color: rgba(18, 32, 47, 0.28);
        text-underline-offset: 4px;
        transition:
          color 160ms ease,
          text-decoration-color 160ms ease;
      }

      .contact-link:hover {
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration-color: currentColor;
      }

      .language-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 1px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: var(--line);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .message {
        min-height: auto;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 28px;
        padding: clamp(26px, 4vw, 44px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      }

      .language {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1;
        font-weight: 750;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      }

      h2 {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(24px, 2.4vw, 34px);
        line-height: 1.05;
        letter-spacing: 0;
        font-weight: 760;
      }

      .copy {
        display: grid;
        gap: 16px;
        max-width: 760px;
      }

      .copy p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: clamp(16px, 1.45vw, 18px);
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .date {
        color: var(--ink);
        font-weight: 720;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        main {
          align-items: start;
        }

        .brand {
          align-items: flex-start;
          flex-direction: column;
        }

        .header-actions {
          justify-content: flex-start;
        }

        .language-grid {
          border-radius: 22px;
        }

        .message {
          gap: 32px;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 520px) {
        main {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .status {
          width: 100%;
          justify-content: center;
          white-space: normal;
          text-align: center;
        }

        .message {
          padding: 24px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="notice" aria-label="Temporary online sales suspension">
        <header class="brand">
          <h1 class="brand-name">
            <img
              class="brand-logo"
              src="https://www.farmae.it/cdn/shop/files/logo-farmae.svg?v=1762777459&amp;width=150"
              alt="Farmae"
            >
          </h1>
          <div class="header-actions">
            <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:contact@farmae.eu">contact@farmae.eu</a>
            <div class="status">New online store coming soon</div>
          </div>
        </header>

        <div class="language-grid">

          <article class="message" lang="es">
            <div class="copy">
              <h2>LAS VENTAS ONLINE ESTÁN TEMPORALMENTE SUSPENDIDAS</h2>
              <p>
                Los pedidos realizados hasta el
                <span class="date">08/05/2026</span> serán procesados con normalidad.
              </p>
              <p>
                Le invitamos a volver a visitarnos en los próximos días para
                descubrir nuestra nueva tienda online actualizada.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="message" lang="fr">
            <div class="copy">
              <h2>LES VENTES EN LIGNE SONT TEMPORAIREMENT SUSPENDUES</h2>
              <p>
                Les commandes effectuées jusqu’au
                <span class="date">08/05/2026</span> seront traitées normalement.
              </p>
              <p>
                Nous vous invitons à revenir nous rendre visite dans les prochains
                jours pour découvrir notre nouvelle boutique en ligne mise à jour.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="message" lang="en">
            <div class="copy">
              <h2>ONLINE SALES ARE TEMPORARILY SUSPENDED</h2>
              <p>
                Orders placed until <span class="date">08/05/2026</span> will be
                processed regularly.
              </p>
              <p>
                We invite you to visit us again in the coming days to discover our
                new updated online store.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
